WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:10.000
The video shows the Issue Reports module screen with its statistics cards.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:20.000
Click on New report, fill in the form with equipment, subject, and description, and save.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:28.000
Then the status change to Resolved from the history table is shown.

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:36.000
Finally, Register maintenance is used to record a maintenance action.
